t face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><br>        <br>        You come expecting an accordion-violin duo&#8230;<br>        and what you get is an African singer accompanied by a kora player.<br>        <br>        You come expecting an accordionist and an alto player...<br>        and you find yourself in clogs dancing a funny gig in the rustic countryside&#8230;<br>        <br>        An ethnic swinging melody&#8230;<br>        changes into a wild improvisation with strange rhythmic beats.<br>        <br>        These two singular musicians so anxious to commune with others fill up         their jerky music creations with acoustic jaunty deviations and outlandish         humor.<br>        <br>        MAM lets out emotions and its energy is catching.<br>        <br>        Have a nice trip!</font></p>      </td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td height="35"></td>    <td></td>  </tr></table>